      public Invoice(ShopSetting header, String customerName, String phoneNumber, String invoiceDate, ArrayList<Item> items, double totalAmount)
      Constructor for creating a new Invoice object.
      Parameters:
      header - The header information for the shop or business.
      customerName - Name of the customer who made the purchase.
      phoneNumber - Phone number of the customer.
      invoiceDate - Date when the purchase was made.
      items - List of items purchased.
      totalAmount - Total amount of the purchase.
